title: The Penguin Book of Limericks - E.O. Parrott; AZW3, EPUB
description:
The Penguin Book of Limericks - Compiled by E.O. Parrott, 1983
Mostly fiction. Tags: Humor, Limericks, Poetry. 

800 humorous poems about history, religion, politics, mathematics, psychology, and sex. A sample:

A pansy who lived in Khartoum
Took a lesbian up to his room;
  And they argued all night
  As to who had the right
To do what and with which and to whom
